  "remarks": "Valeriy Shatilo held the position of Director of OJSC 2566 Plant for the Repair of Radio-Electronic Weapons until February 2025. The enterprise specialises in the repair and modernisation of weapons and air defence equipment, as well as other complex radio-electronic equipment and military products. OJSC 2566 Radioelectronic Armament Repair Plant is providing maintenance and repair services to the Russian Armed Forces.",
